word_mean_info__list.difference: 多指某一种形式的物质，既可指元素也可指化合物。
多用于日常生活中，非正式用词。常指构成整体的所有部分、物体或项目。有时指劣等材料，含轻蔑意味。
通常指构成实物的物质，与精神相对立。在科学上，指占有空间，并能以某种方式被感官觉察的一切东西。
通常指组成客观存在物的部分或其原料。

bilingual.source: She bought some new stuff for her kitchen.

bilingual.source: Don't forget to bring your stuff for the trip.

bilingual.source: Can you hand me that stuff on the table?

bilingual.source: I need to pack my stuff before we leave.
bilingual.target: 我们离开之前我需要收拾我的东西。

bilingual.source: The food at this restaurant is really good stuff.

bilingual.source: He always brings some good stuff to the parties.

list.abstract: 《Stuff》是英国最大的私人出版集团Haymarket的旗下杂志，主要报道时尚科技酷品，向读者传递什么是当下最新潮、最热门的玩意儿。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. Here's a box of your stuff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，这一盒是你的东西。

yingyinNormal.en: That is exactly why I do not lend you stuff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我才不借给你东西！

yingyinNormal.en: Wow, you really like all this space stuff?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你很喜欢太空的东西，是吧？

yingyinNormal.en: No. Well, I cannot give this stuff away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不要。呃，这些东西怎么送也送不出去。

yingyinNormal.en: It's grownup stuff. You wouldn't understand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这都是成年人的东西，你理解不了的。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't try to make me uncomfortable with feminine stuff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别想用女人的东西来唬我。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, I've never played my stuff for anyone before.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的东西没有弹给别人听过。

yingyinNormal.en: It's fun talking to you, Leonard. I always learn stuff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 跟你说话真有趣，莱纳德，总学得到东西。

yingyinNormal.en: What stuff? Monica's chicken parm. I'll take care of it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么东西？莫妮卡的奶酪鸡，我得把它解决掉。

yingyinNormal.en: It doesn't go with any of my stuff. Well, what about my stuff?
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，它与我的东西都不搭配。那么我的东西呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Watch out! Whoa! Oh, my good. A T. Rex. Get your stuff. Get your stuff. Get it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当心，当心。哦，天啊，霸王龙! 快收拾好东西，收拾好东西，快点。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry. You know, I have to ask for stuff that we really need, stuff that he can get easily.
yingyinNormal.zh: 抱歉，我得要我们真正需要的东西，他很容易就能弄到的东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me. Do you know anything about this stuff? I know everything about this stuff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 打扰一下，你了解这个东西吗？我了解它的一切。

yingyinNormal.en: What a lot of stuff! We must be careful not to forget anything when we go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这么多的东西。我们必须小心，别把东西落下拉。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, what's going on? He got all of his stuff stolen.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么了？他的东西全被偷了。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's grab our stuff and get the hell out of here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们快把东西拿一拿，离开这里吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Crazy stuff, bragging, crazy stuff, karaoke. No, see, I don't see anything useful here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 极度自恋，疯狂自恋，卡拉OK，不，我在这没得到任何有用的东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Hi. Hi. Hi darling. So, what's this. Some of your old stuff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的这是什么？你以前的东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, are you going to get a handyman to install this stuff?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要找人帮忙安装这些东西吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. You want to start loading this stuff into the truck?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，要开始把这些东西搬上货车吗？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
